{
  "Title": "An update for ruby is now available for openEuler-20.03-LTS-SP4,openEuler-22.03-LTS-SP4,openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP1,openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP3",
  "Type": "Security Advisory",
  "Publisher": {
